<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Wolfein Eclipse Trigger -->
  <Wolfein_EclipseTrigger.label>月蝕激發劑</Wolfein_EclipseTrigger.label>
  <!-- EN: A specialized enhancement serum developed by the MegaCorp specifically for the Wolfein. It forcibly activates their latent physical functions during non-full moon periods. To ensure combat stability, all addictive components have been removed from the formula. Due to its mechanism being deeply reliant on the unique physiology of the Wolfein, use by other species is typically ineffective—or may trigger unpredictable side effects.-->
  <Wolfein_EclipseTrigger.description>由軍企專為沃芬族設計的強化藥劑，可在非滿月期間強制激發其潛在身體機能，為確保戰鬥人員的穩定性，製劑已剔除潛在成癮成分。因其機制深度依賴沃芬族特有的生理結構，其他種族使用后通常無效，或引發不可預測的副作用。</Wolfein_EclipseTrigger.description>
  <!-- EN: Inject {0} -->
  <Wolfein_EclipseTrigger.ingestible.ingestCommandString>注射 {0}</Wolfein_EclipseTrigger.ingestible.ingestCommandString>
  <!-- EN: Injecting {0}. -->
  <Wolfein_EclipseTrigger.ingestible.ingestReportString>注射中 {0}</Wolfein_EclipseTrigger.ingestible.ingestReportString>
  
